5.1 Nondimensionalization
Consider the scaling \[\begin{eqnarray*}
x^\ast = x \sqrt{\frac \rho {D_n}} , \qquad t^\ast = \rho \, t , \quad u^\ast = \frac uK, \quad n^\ast = n \frac \alpha \rho
